stimulus:
We need to check your headphones or speakers are working well enough for the experiment to run.

When you click continue you will hear a voice name a colour and you will be asked to identify the colour.
Great, that worked; just one more check!
Press continue to start the experiment! The word streams will start after you press continue
We will now ask you some additional questions.
In the last stream of words you hear any two-word phrases?

responses: {"Q0":"Send sheep her weep cold rich fat small tall feet"}
{"Q0":"They all sounded quite similar and I'm having trouble distinguishing the earlier streams from the later ones"}

{"Q0":"It was interesting and I was really concentrating on the words but to be honest I think the robotic voice used made it quite difficult. I think because of it being robotic and very fast, I couldn't actually understand what a few of the words were and some of them seemed to blend straight into the next word which made it difficult"}
